        "content": "<p>Jerod is joined by Carson Gross, the creator of htmx –a small, zero-dependency JavaScript library that he says, \"completes HTML as a hypertext\". Carson built it because he's big on hypermedia, he even wrote a book called Hypermedia Systems. Carson has a lot of strong opinions weakly held that we dive into in this conversation. <span aria-label=\"link\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f517\" role=\"img\" title=\"link\">:link:</span> <a href=\"https://changelog.fm/646\">https://changelog.fm/646</a></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Ch</th>\n<th>Start</th>\n<th>Title</th>\n<th>Runs</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>01</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.fm/646#t=0\">00:00</a></td>\n<td>This week on The Changelog</td>\n<td>01:17</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>02</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.fm/646#t=77\">01:17</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://retool.com/agents\">Sponsor: Retool</a></td>\n<td>01:59</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>03</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.fm/646#t=196\">03:16</a></td>\n<td>Start the show!</td>\n<td>00:59</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>04</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.fm/646#t=255\">04:15</a></td>\n<td>Getting htmx attention</td>\n<td>04:53</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>05</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.fm/646#t=548\">09:08</a></td>\n<td>Viewpoint origins</td>\n<td>03:32</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>06</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.fm/646#t=759\">12:39</a></td>\n<td>Hypermedia distilled</td>\n<td>02:18</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>07</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.fm/646#t=897\">14:57</a></td>\n<td>Why html lacks</td>\n<td>03:52</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>08</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.fm/646#t=1129\">18:49</a></td>\n<td>What htmx adds</td>\n<td>04:38</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>09</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.fm/646#t=1407\">23:27</a></td>\n<td>Echoes of jQuery</td>\n<td>06:02</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://changelog.fm/646#t=1769\">29:29</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"https://depot.dev\">Sponsor: